            <date when-iso="1796-07-08">1796. July. 8.</date>
            Abr. <rs type="person" ref="#JAS">Schlesinger</rs>
            pro 130 Reichsthaler Friedrichs d'or.
         </p>
         <p resp="otherHand">
            16 Groschen incl. Stpl. bezahlt.
         </p>
